[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Analysis[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter examining the code and evaluation report, I've identified the root cause of [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe persistent OOM issue:[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Root Cause[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe issue is not with the validation ranges added in the previous patch, but with a[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfundamental design problem:[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **The SINGLETON Pattern Problem**: `[0m[1;35mCompressorStreamFactory.getSingleton[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreturns a singleton instance created with the default constructor, which sets [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`memoryLimitInKb = [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mno memory limit[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Memory Check Bypass**: In `[0m[1;35mLZWInputStream.initializeTables[0m[1;39m([0m[39mmaxCodeSize, [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmemoryLimiKiB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` at line [0m[1;36m210[0m[39m, there's a conditional check: `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmemoryLimiKiB > [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m-1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`. When `memoryLimiKiB` is `[0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m`, this entire memory protection block is [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**skipped**.[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Unprotected Allocation**: The allocation at line [0m[1;36m186[0m[39m proceeds without any [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmemory check when `memoryLimiKiB = [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m`, allowing even [0m[32m"valid"[0m[39m `maxCodeSize` values [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[1;36m9[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m30[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to cause massive allocations:[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - [0m[33mmaxCodeSize[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m16[0m[39m: ~[0m[1;36m384[0m[39m KiB [0m[1;39m([0m[39mreasonable[0m[1;39m)[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - [0m[33mmaxCodeSize[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m20[0m[39m: ~[0m[1;36m6[0m[39m MB [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlarge but manageable[0m[1;39m)[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - [0m[33mmaxCodeSize[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m30[0m[39m: ~[0m[1;36m6[0m[39m GB [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcauses OOM[0m[1;39m)[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Previous Patch Ineffective**: The previous patch added range validation [0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m9[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m30[0m[1;39m][0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfor Z format and [0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m8[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m30[0m[1;39m][0m[39m for LZW, but these ranges still permit [0m[33mmaxCodeSize[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m30[0m[39m, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhich requires ~[0m[1;36m6[0m[39m GB. The validation passed, but the allocation still exhausted [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmemory because no memory limit was enforced.[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Why the Patch Failed[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe previous patch correctly identified the need for range validation, but didn't [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maddress that even [0m[32m"valid"[0m[39m values within those ranges can cause OOM when no memory [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlimit is enforced. The line number changes [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m220[0m[39m→[0m[1;36m223[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m86[0m[39m→[0m[1;36m90[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m confirm the patch was [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mapplied, but the OOM still occurs at line [0m[1;36m186[0m[39m because the memory check was never [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexecuted.[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fix requires modifying `[0m[1;35mLZWInputStream.initializeTables[0m[1;39m([0m[39mmaxCodeSize, [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmemoryLimiKiB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to enforce a reasonable default memory limit even when [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`memoryLimiKiB = [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m`.[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Implementation Steps[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**File: [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`src/main/java/org/apache/commons/compress/compressors/lzw/LZWInputStream.java`**[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Step [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m**: Modify the `[0m[1;35minitializeTables[0m[1;39m([0m[39mint maxCodeSize, int memoryLimiKiB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmethod [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround lines [0m[1;36m205[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m221[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to:[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Define a reasonable default memory limit constant [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m MB = [0m[1;36m102[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m400[0m[39m KiB[0m[1;39m)[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - When `memoryLimiKiB == [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m`, use the default limit instead of bypassing the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcheck[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Always perform the memory limit check with the effective limit[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Throw `MemoryLimitException` if the required memory exceeds the effective [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlimit[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Step [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m**: The memory calculation and validation should:[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Calculate `maxTableSize` using long to prevent overflow: `long maxTableSize = [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m1L << maxCodeSize`[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Calculate memory usage: `memoryUsageBytes = maxTableSize * [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m`[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Convert to KiB: `memoryUsageKiB = memoryUsageBytes >> [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m`[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Compare against the effective limit[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Step [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m**: Remove the conditional `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmemoryLimiKiB > [0m[1;36m-1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` guard, replacing it [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith logic that uses an effective limit.[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Code Logic[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotected void [0m[1;35minitializeTables[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfinal int maxCodeSize, final int memoryLimiKiB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthrows MemoryLimitException [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmaxCodeSize <= [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mIllegalArgumentException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"maxCodeSize is "[0m[39m + maxCodeSize + [0m[32m", [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mmust be bigger than 0"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Define a reasonable default memory limit: [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m MB[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m This allows maxCodeSize up to ~[0m[1;36m16[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m17[0m[39m, which is sufficient for most [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlegitimate files[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    final int DEFAULT_MEMORY_LIMIT_KIB = [0m[1;36m102400[0m[39m; [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m MB[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Use the default limit when no limit is specified[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    final int effectiveMemoryLimit = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmemoryLimiKiB == [0m[1;36m-1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m ? [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDEFAULT_MEMORY_LIMIT_KIB : memoryLimiKiB;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Prevent overflow in calculation by using long[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmaxCodeSize > [0m[1;36m30[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mIllegalArgumentException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"maxCodeSize "[0m[39m + maxCodeSize + [0m[32m" is too [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mlarge and would cause overflow"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    final long maxTableSize = 1L << maxCodeSize;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    final long memoryUsageBytes = maxTableSize * [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m; [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m4[0m[39m for prefixes + [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m for [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcharacters + [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m for outputStack[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    final long memoryUsageKiB = memoryUsageBytes >> [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmemoryUsageKiB > effectiveMemoryLimit[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mMemoryLimitException[0m[1;39m([0m[39mmemoryUsageKiB, effectiveMemoryLimit[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35minitializeTables[0m[1;39m([0m[39mmaxCodeSize[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Rationale[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Default Protection**: By enforcing a [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m MB default limit, we protect against [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mOOM attacks while allowing legitimate compressed files to be processed. This is [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbased on the test suite using [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m GB [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m048[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m576[0m[39m KiB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m as a reasonable limit.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Backward Compatibility**: Code that explicitly sets memory limits continues to[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwork as before. Only code using the SINGLETON or passing `[0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m` gets the new default [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprotection.[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Memory Calculation**:[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - [0m[33mmaxCodeSize[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m16[0m[39m: [0m[1;36m384[0m[39m KiB [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwell within [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m MB[0m[1;39m)[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - [0m[33mmaxCodeSize[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m17[0m[39m: [0m[1;36m768[0m[39m KiB [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwithin [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m MB[0m[1;39m)[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - [0m[33mmaxCodeSize[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m18[0m[39m: [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m536[0m[39m KiB = [0m[1;36m1.5[0m[39m MB [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwithin [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m MB[0m[1;39m)[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - [0m[33mmaxCodeSize[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m19[0m[39m: [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m MB [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwithin [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m MB[0m[1;39m)[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - [0m[33mmaxCodeSize[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m20[0m[39m: [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m MB [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwithin [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m MB[0m[1;39m)[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - [0m[33mmaxCodeSize[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m21[0m[39m: [0m[1;36m12[0m[39m MB [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwithin [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m MB[0m[1;39m)[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - [0m[33mmaxCodeSize[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m30[0m[39m: [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m291[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m456[0m[39m KiB = ~[0m[1;36m6[0m[39m GB [0m[1;39m([0m[39mREJECTED[0m[1;39m)[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Format Compatibility**: The Z format specification allows maxCodeSize up to [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m31[0m[39m, but practical implementations [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlike UnshrinkingInputStream with [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [33mMAX_CODE_SIZE[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m13[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m use much lower limits. The [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m MB default allows maxCodeSize up [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto about [0m[1;36m20[0m[39m, which is sufficient for legitimate files while preventing abuse.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Overflow Protection**: Using `long` for calculations prevents integer overflow[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhen computing `maxTableSize` and `memoryUsageBytes`.[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **No Fuzzer/Harness Modification**: This fix operates entirely within the [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibrary's decompression logic and doesn't modify any fuzzing harness or test code.[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Preservation of Existing Logic[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The validation in the single-argument `[0m[1;35minitializeTables[0m[1;39m([0m[39mmaxCodeSize[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` remains [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munchanged[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The array allocation logic and initialization loops remain unchanged  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The decompression algorithms in ZCompressorInputStream remain unchanged[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Tests can still override the limit by creating CompressorStreamFactory with [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mspecific memoryLimitInKb values[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The MemoryLimitException mechanism remains the same[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Side Effects and Mitigation[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Potential Side Effect**: Legitimate files with maxCodeSize > [0m[1;36m20[0m[39m might be rejected[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith the [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m MB default.[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Mitigation**: [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Users processing such files can create a CompressorStreamFactory with a higher [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmemory limit[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The exception message clearly indicates the memory limit can be increased[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This is preferable to OOM crashes, which provide no recovery mechanism[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Testing Compatibility**: The existing test `[0m[1;35mtestInvalidMaxCodeSize[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` uses [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m GB [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlimit explicitly, so it won't be affected by the [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m MB default.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m[01/09/26 21:10:07][0m[2;36m [0m[34mINFO    [0m Prism Supervisor Routing: TeamStatus.EVALUATE -> TeamStatus.END                      ]8;id=440974;file:///home/qqor/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py\[2m__init__.py[0m]8;;\[2m:[0m]8;id=453848;file:///home/qqor/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py#160\[2m160[0m]8;;\
[2;36m                    [0m         [1m([0mn evals: [1;36m3[0m, patch status: PatchStatus.SOUND[1m)[0m                                        [2m               [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [35mlta-02_vuln_9/[0m[95magent-output-1767993007.0308924[0m                                        [2m               [0m
